      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows some clear signs of use, including a few noticeable door dings, faded paint on the roof, and a small crack in the rear bumper cover. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining on the passenger seat and typical wear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future to stay in top shape. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been maintained regularly but is showing its age.",
