    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, making it the perfect choice if you want something dependable that still looks great on the road. It drives nice and smooth, and I\u2019ve taken good care of it over the years. I'm looking for a quick and easy sale, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29900.0,
